@node Main "Bobarr - Documentation"

                              'Bobarr' 1.1

                           by Charles-N. Jacob

  'Bobarr' is a @{" Workbench game " link play} where you have to move all the
bars that are shown on the 7 by 7 spaces board. It is based on the
usual 'Sliding-bars' puzzles, but Bobarr offers a variation: in
addition to horizontal and vertical bars, there are also diagonal
bars that have to be moved. Each type of bar can be moved in the
directions its shape represent... if the empty space is located in
line and next to that bar.

  Another feature is that any bar located at the edge of the board
can move to the other side... if, of course, the empty space is on
the other side and in line with that bar.

  Complete the game in the least amount of moves possible.

  Have fun!

